{"tid":1419316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正反方巿民 港鐵開「論壇」","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:31:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"617b99f0b4bec00586b114be3493da26c5c1ecbf","tid":1419316,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:50:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190806/s00001/1565030069583/%e6%ad%a3%e5%8f%8d%e6%96%b9%e5%b7%bf%e6%b0%91-%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e9%96%8b%e3%80%8c%e8%ab%96%e5%a3%87%e3%80%8d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565030069583%2F%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e5%258f%258d%25e6%2596%25b9%25e5%25b7%25bf%25e6%25b0%2591-%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e9%2596%258b%25e3%2580%258c%25e8%25ab%2596%25e5%25a3%2587%25e3%2580%258d&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=a9c560ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565030069583%2F%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e5%258f%258d%25e6%2596%25b9%25e5%25b7%25bf%25e6%25b0%2591-%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e9%2596%258b%25e3%2580%258c%25e8%25ab%2596%25e5%25a3%2587%25e3%2580%258d&h=ce6cce14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190806/s00001/1565030069583/%e6%ad%a3%e5%8f%8d%e6%96%b9%e5%b7%bf%e6%b0%91-%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e9%96%8b%e3%80%8c%e8%ab%96%e5%a3%87%e3%80%8d</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】昨早不少上班族無法如常上班，有人在港鐵站內吃早餐，也有不同立場乘客圍起開「城市論壇」。<br />\n<br />\n要過海工作的鄭小姐，昨原計劃到紅磡坐巴士，但見紅隧車龍塞至漆咸道，因此改乘港鐵，但到紅磡站又見職員稱服務暫停，請乘客改乘巴士，她只好放棄工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另邊廂，在港鐵服務暫停下，多個車站有乘客與示威者口角。其中約10時半在黃大仙港鐵站閘口，有年長女子投訴無法看醫生，大罵示威者激進；有男長者走向該女子面前說：「你估邊個造成？一個人造成㗎！」圍觀者拍掌。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">其後，黃大仙站出現「城市論壇」，反對示威者的中年男子說：「你哋後生仔未捱過，點知揾食艱難。」等待列車重開上班的年輕人回應：「我怕咩？我爛命一條！反正點都買唔到樓。」該中年男子則說：「每個人也可以找到自己方法生存，唔一定好似𠵱家咁（示威及不合作運動）。」另一男長者搭口：「新疆啲人都生存緊㗎！」中年男子無語，稍後離開了。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d54c894a036856985f9da02966597b8ff5764b7e","tid":1419316,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>長輩連儂牆大勝</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a8cca5872dbfd6fd0c606b4c76b72a6819306343","tid":1419316,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:56:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>文宣組盡做唔該</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1a2523b9df1178510432ff505ec506d8016420e5","tid":1419316,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"【置頂】被內地國安打到下頷骨折的人 給香港人的一封信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418607</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca8e8474992c80e3207f34191f640823cace1fbd","tid":1419316,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"另一男長者搭口：「新疆啲人都生存緊㗎！」中年男子無語，稍後離開了。"},{"pid":"07e15c78f7bb872d744c5a1418408693c35d36f9","tid":1419316,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d58dfd148a4deed69ccf339d3533f47bfa7e1317","tid":1419316,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}